# Showcase Website: Claw Ecosystem

This plan detail the creation of a premium, single-file [index.html](file:///Users/mkazi/claw-ecosystem/index.html) showcase for the entire Claw Ecosystem.

## UI/UX Design Goals
- **Aesthetic**: Premium Dark Mode, Glassmorphism, Dynamic Gradients.
- **Interactivity**: Smooth scroll animations, hover effects, and expanded agent dossiers.
- **Single File**: All CSS and JS will be embedded for portability.
- **Performance**: Use CSS Grid/Flexbox and lightweight CSS animations.

## v2 Enhancement Goals (Deep Dive)
- **Data Density**: Include full skill catalogs and detailed workflow logic for all 5 agents.
- **Deep Linking**: Add clickable links to actual project files (READMEs, SKILL.md, workflows).
- **Methodology Viz**: Visual breakdowns of RALPH (OpenClaw) and HEARTBEAT (PicoClaw).
- **Documentation**: Direct links to `docs/` folders and setup guides.
- **Economic Model**: Showcase the "ClawWork Coworker" cost tracking logic.

